dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded by ITOS from an email sent by the IMO. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following errors were found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Admin3 units in new Admin1 North Western have been given new p-codes with SL05 attribution 2. The border for new Admin1 "North Western" cut Admin3 unit "Gbanti Kamarank" in half. As instructed by IMO, Admin3 "Gbanti Kamarank" was given attribution for Admin1 "Northern". 3. Admin3 layer was given the more detailed national border from Admin0-2.
